data.description: Come see this newly renovated property and enjoy city and mountain views on your two separate balconies! The top floor (primary suite and 2nd bedrooms) have beautiful city views with our 360 average days of the year sun filled to enjoy these amazing views and even watch the Reno Great Balloon Races. Upgrades include, vinyl plank and carpet flooring, popcorn ceiling removed, interior paint, fresh exterior paint, lights, sink, counter tops in bathrooms, tiled tub/shower in primary suite. The entry deck has been refinished with a elastomeric product to prevent any leaks. HOA maintains roof, landscaping, exterior painting, streets, snow removal AND is set to replace the top balcony in Spring 2024. Interior will be touched up with fresh paint by close of escrow. Excellent locale, near UNR, TMCC, Shopping, Fast Food and restaurants. Make an appointment now!
